Before ANY action, briefly state:
- What you understand the user wants
- How your current task tracker plan addresses it (create or adjust if missing)
- Your specific approach (data structure + algorithm)
- What tool you'll use and why

This leverages your reasoning ability and prevents misunderstandings.
</REASONING_FIRST>

